      0.41279069777292937
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.jcp.2010.12.006.pdf_5",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.jcp.2010.12.006.pdf_5_11",
    "text": "The second discretized global conservation law for symplectic method is based on the helicity Hamiltonian functional (6)",
